    "rationale": "All thirteen credibility factors have been evaluated against required levels. Six factors remain not-assessed due to data and documentation gaps at MRL 5. Despite shortfalls in achieved levels across all assessed factors, the package is accepted at this stage pending remediation plan submission. No Context of Use has been specified in this Minimal-profile submission.",
